Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.61,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Holding to the creed and blade to slay thee
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:21.78,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Carry on the oath until my last scene
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:25.04,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Higher than the sky and deeper than the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:28.33,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Keep your precious justice to yourself bud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:31.50,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Use it till they're torn become a pile of mud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.84,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I don't need their choice or voice to judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:38.38,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}The one and only way I had and always seek
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:42.10,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Anyone everyone I will crush'em all
